_:Nd456829740514e05b8836f886587930d <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The UK condemns the drone and missile strikes targeting the United Arab Emirates. </p>\n\n<p>As I set out during my visit to the region last month, stability in the Gulf directly affects the UK.</p>\n\n<p>We stand in solidarity with the UAE and will continue to support the defence of our partners in the Gulf. </p>\n\n<p>This escalation must cease. Iran needs to engage meaningfully in negotiations to ensure the ceasefire in the Middle East endures, and a long-term diplomatic solution is achieved.</p>\n</div>" .
